UAL CORP; ACQUISITIONS; UNITED AIRLINES; WOLF, STEPHEN M; DAVIS, MARVIN; 
INTERNATIONAL ASSOCIATION OF MACHINISTS; PETERPAUL, JOHN F; AIRLINES -- UNITED 
STATES 
</P>
