<P>
Photo, Measure M advocates Tom Rogers, left side from left, Bruce Nestande and 
Thomas Riley square off against Russ Burkett, Sandra Genis and Lester Berriman 
during taping. Jim Cooper moderated. GLENN KOENIG/ Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
