<SUBJECT>
<P>
SECURITIES INDUSTRY -- LAYOFFS; PROFITS 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA101889-0134 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 122302 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
October 18, 1989, Wednesday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
